Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP Start
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:16.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:20.60,OP6,,0,0,0,,Humans aren't such a big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:25.44,OP6,,0,0,0,,Who needs tomorrow anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:28.71,OP6,,0,0,0,,so don't hide your fists
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.65,0:00:32.92,OP6,,0,0,0,,You're not old enough
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:39.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,to sell your dreams away to uncertainty
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:44.66,OP6,,0,0,0,,Hey boys, you're the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:48.26,OP6,,0,0,0,,who can pull the trigger in your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.64,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're living in this senseless, ridiculous,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:59.01,OP6,,0,0,0,,awesome world right at this moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:01.48,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:07.35,OP6,,0,0,0,,Don't forget every truth or lie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.76,0:01:11.08,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.08,0:01:13.42,OP6,,0,0,0,,We're way too young to die
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.42,0:01:18.29,OP6,,0,0,0,,In this empty town lined with empty faces
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.56,OP6,,0,0,0,,All the kids took off
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:23.10,OP6,,0,0,0,,into this windless night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.10,0:01:29.00,OP6,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3000)}Because they want to change something
Comment: 0,0:01:31.04,0:01:31.07,OP6,,0,0,0,,OP End
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.64,0:01:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, you've woken up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.16,0:01:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a hindrance back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but it won't be like\Nthat this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you...\Nthe true power of Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine... Then I'll go all out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.09,0:02:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You take a good look\Nwith your Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,at my Way of Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.55,0:02:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me by just pointlessly...\Nincreasing the number!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You little--!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.70,0:02:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can spot the real body in\None shot with my Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.74,0:02:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I deliberately went along\Nwith your game...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't go easy on you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.72,0:03:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:28.06,Sign_1,,0,0,0,,{\bord3\blur4\fad(600,0)\pos(611,551)\3c&H000000&}Father and Son\NThe Broken Family Crest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What was up...\Nwith those eyes of Big Brother's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't...\Njust an ordinary Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.03,0:04:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And... quite a bit of time's\Npassed since then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but things are still kind of awkward\Nbetween him and Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... how have things\Nbeen going at the Academy lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's boring with just school classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always number one, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.89,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the fundamental\NJutsu of the Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.76,0:05:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sign is as I taught you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You build up Chakra,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.69,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,stop it once at around between\Nthe mouth and the chest area,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and spew it out at once after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... is teaching me Jutsu himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally... Father has also recognized me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I must live up to his expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.25,0:06:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I too can...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.75,0:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, it won't go like\Nit did with Itachi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've still been\Ntoo soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A member of the Uchiha Clan\Nis not recognized as full-fledged
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,until they can use the Fire Style.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.54,0:07:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The Uchiha crest...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,means those who possess\Nthe Uchiha that controls fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.99,0:08:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.85,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure enough, it won't go\Nlike it did with Itachi, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It might've still been\Ntoo soon for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just, getting started.\NDamn it! One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time...\NPlease join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still too soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.63,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I were to teach you\Nfor only after a week...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.47,0:09:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten... the hang of the Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want you to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Failure is not an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire Style: Fire Ball Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.88,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, improve yourself\Nand soar large
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.98,0:11:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so as not to bring shame\Nto the crest on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.84,0:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And... Iet me say one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't chase after\Nyour older brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Father really think of\NBig Brother and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The other day, Father said to me,\N"That's my boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.74,0:12:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd always said that only\Nto Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.00,0:12:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So I was really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But lately, Father and Brother\Nhaven't been getting along, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,that I might just be\Na replacement for Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.52,0:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Your older brother's your older brother.\NAnd you are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.80,0:13:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father cares deeply\Nabout you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.47,0:13:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why does he only think\Nabout Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father has to protect\Nthe Uchiha Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,as a representative of the clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.16,0:13:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi is just bigger than you\Nand is your elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll naturally be entrusted
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.76,0:13:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,with that much more work\Nfor the clan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Your father is the supervisor\Nof the work, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it might be that his eyes were\Nlikely to go towards your older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, this is just between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.36,0:13:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,your father does nothing\Nbut talk about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.37,0:13:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just always sullen\Nand awkward, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up to Big Brother\Nno matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother's back is still\Nfar out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sasuke...\NMaybe another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.86,0:15:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Clan... Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You measure incorrectly\Nthe size of your own "vessels"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't know the depth of mine,\Nso you grovel there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My "vessel" is\Ndismayed at this foolish clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like... ever since that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he hasn't been the same\Nas he was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.18,0:15:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,T oday, when school's finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,will you join me for\Nsome Shuriken Jutsu training?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.57,0:15:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm busy.\NYou should have Father teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But even I know that you're better\Nat Shuriken Jutsu than Father is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You always treat me like\Na nuisance like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, Sasuke.\NMaybe next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the time to\Nbe dealing with you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You always say, "Forgive me, Sasuke,"\Nand poke me on the forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say "today,"\Nbut it never happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness...\Nhe's the same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes looking back\Nat Father that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't just an ordinary Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are there several types\Nof Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... You're already interested\Nin Sharingan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.01,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's still too soon for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.18,0:17:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally different from\Nthe Fire Style Jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But someday, I too...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.77,0:17:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all... I'm your kid, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.78,0:17:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there is a Visual Jutsu\Nabove the Sharingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.86,0:18:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the Mangekyo Sharingan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mangekyo Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In the long history of the Uchiha,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a legendary Visual Jutsu\Nthat only a few develop.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's said that it only opened\Nunder a particular condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A particular condition...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't chase after your\Nolder brother anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he thinks of my\Nrelationship with Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why doesn't Big Brother care\Nabout me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a bit peculiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:19:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a type of person who doesn't\Ncare for making friends with people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.09,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.85,0:19:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.06,0:19:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I, his father, can't read that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I spoke because I wanted\Nmore of Big Brother's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.04,0:19:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Father isn't against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.32,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Sasuke!\NYour box lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch your Shuriken practice\Nafter you come home.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.87,0:19:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not practice, it's training!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.96,0:19:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that Father dislikes\NBig Brother, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.55,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Brother graduated from the Academy\Nat the top of his class at age seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He learned to use\Nthe Sharingan at age eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And he was promoted\Nto Chunin at age ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I've got the same Uchiha blood\Nflowing inside me as he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not gonna tell me this is\Nthe best you can do, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You boast about your Way of Ninja\Nand this is all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still thinking that\NI'm a member of your comrade game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.18,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.83,0:20:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a hopeless fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop wasting time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me all you've got,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.82,0:20:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you number one hyperactive,\Nknucklehead Ninja!
Comment: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:08.08,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED Start
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:18.37,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}When I recalled the parts one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.37,0:21:24.74,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I felt as though I had understood everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.74,0:21:35.31,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Faded words which I kept so close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:45.09,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Speechless nights, a hint of warmth,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:51.83,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}and this distant yearning for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.14,0:22:01.14,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}I live, simply repeating this cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.32,0:22:12.85,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Held in my two hands is a droplet of time
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.30,0:22:23.30,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}Softly clutching forgotten memories, lost words
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.18,0:22:37.10,ED9,,0,0,0,,{\blur8}{\fad(0,2500)}I'll keep these thoughts...
Comment: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:38.10,ED9,,0,0,0,,ED End
